Attribute confidential is responded to by parameter Issue with a description: Updates an issue to be confidential. At least one of the following parameters is required for the request to be successful: assignee_id, assignee_ids, confidential, created_at, description, discussion_locked, due_date, labels, milestone_id, state_event, title
